00:21:19,207 --> 00:21:21,009
within ourselves of matter.

209
00:21:23,393 --> 00:21:23,512
Yeah?

210
00:21:23,532 --> 00:21:29,603
So, I mean, this is what you can explore a bit in your practice.

211
00:21:29,623 --> 00:21:31,865
And then finally, there's the charnel grounds.

212
00:21:32,887 --> 00:21:33,828
I think there are nine.

213
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:43,222
There are nine where you go and sit at the charnel ground, because in those days, they would just leave the body out, you know, dressed in white robes.

214
00:21:43,557 --> 00:21:50,076
And it was these white robes that the ascetics would take, the samanas would take, and make robes out of them.

215
00:21:50,136 --> 00:21:52,022
And the Buddha himself would have done that.

216
00:21:54,569 --> 00:22:01,751
So they're on the channel devoured by crows, hawks, vultures, dogs, jackals, worms, et cetera.

